{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that could be carried-- nothing of those big ones on wheels-- that could be hand-carried. 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And absolute [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rule against any valuables, any precious stones, any jewelry, anything-- any valuables, in brief.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of the children, with well-meaning but misguided parents, had, had things, valuables, sewn into their clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a stupid and reckless thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can understand it, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is my little one going to do without anything?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's better for the little one to get out alive and poor than with the jewelry and perish in the attempt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our train, there was one commotion that reportedly at the border, when the SS came and searched everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took the suitcases, smashed some of them on the-- just thew them on the platform-- emptied them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Something that apparently for future transports, there were presentations made to the-- representation made to the government.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they apparently stopped the worst of that, for the future transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But on my transport, there was a lot of that going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They searched whom they wanted to, whoever looked suspicious to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who they didn't like the looks of, they would be very brutal about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In my-- in my section, we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing like that happened there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They got the suitcases down but just barely opened them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they just-- ah-- went on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then-- but we-- this commotion reportedly was a boy who had been discovered to have some jewelry in his clothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And reportedly he was taken off the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even whether the story is true, or whether it's the kind of thing that runs-- rumor runs the-- along the train.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
